  "title": "manicurist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will clean, shape, and beautify clients' nails by performing manicures, pedicures, and applying acrylic or gel extensions to enhance nail appearance and client satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Clean clients' nails thoroughly to prepare for treatments</li><li>Shape nails accurately to achieve desired styles and client preferences</li><li>Apply manicures and pedicures following hygiene and quality standards</li><li>Perform acrylic and gel nail extensions with precision to ensure durability and aesthetic appeal</li><li>Maintain a clean and safe work environment throughout all nail services</li></ul>",
